      p Explore each concept interactively:
      .theory-nav-links
        a.theory-nav-link(href='/hash')
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-lock
          | &nbsp; Hash Function
        a.theory-nav-link(href='/block')
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-th-large
          | &nbsp; Block
